ucl.group18.bodyscanner.model

Class MeasurementRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • ucl.group18.bodyscanner.model.MeasurementRequest

  • public class MeasurementRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for a measurement request to the server Has parity with a measurement request record in the MeasurementRequests Database. Holds information on: - Database Unique ID - server request ID - if scan processed by server - time of creation of the request - time of last request to the server - Gender - No of times this request has been made to the server - Measurements (if scan is processed) Created by Shubham on 12/04/2015.
